{"tid":1369469,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"還手唔駛大動作打 試下學柏林用力扭","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:24:08.000Z","uid":190836,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9099607c2f8486442694b94e72ef229a01212d01","tid":1369469,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:58:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不主動攻擊，只自衛還手</span></span><br />\n咁點還手，還到咩地步先啱呢？<br />\n絕對明大家見到手足比人打一定會好嬲，但始終我地要顧及鏡頭，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔同意打死</span>。<br />\n而且我地唔係黑警，唔好同佢地一樣濫用武力！<br />\n但我地都仲有方法令對方痛苦之餘，仲望落冇咁暴力，等cctvb冇得抹黑我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信大家都記得<span style=\"color: red;\">柏林點對手足</span>架啦？<br />\n用遮都有機會傷到自己人，但幾個人按住攻擊者，再<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用手扭</span></span>，咁就遮都唔駛用，仲制服咗個暴徒<br />\n最重要就係<span style=\"color: red;\">，望落唔暴力，似制服暴徒，仲要係令佢更痛！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊唔好打，試下用手扭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d9660eb25d9ec743d6b0209ccdd45ef9dcfb8b48","tid":1369469,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:59:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊唔好打，試下用手扭</span></span>"},{"pid":"2d5923a07e8b3d71f823f993209eae7aa8402bd3","tid":1369469,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">扭到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a3cbd0e9d1ddb80d84e19157f9e64c25561fc4e2","tid":1369469,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"幫手推啊！！"},{"pid":"b429d45a7cb7d872e308d31a707f8d03416b475a","tid":1369469,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":